OL,3,CAlderney islanders fear they will be
OL,4,Cstranded as airport repairs delayed
OL,6,FResidents in fear they could end up
OL,7,Fstranded as repair work at Alderney
OL,8,Fairport has been delayed.
OL,10,FBusiness owner Jo Corder said: "Every
OL,11,Ftime you find a pothole you think how
OL,12,Fclose was that, how dangerous was that?
OL,14,F"Then you see them patch it up and
OL,15,Fthat takes away our flights, the
OL,16,Fflights then aren't happening and
OL,17,Fpeople are disappointed- they are
OL,18,Fsupposed to be travelling."
OL,20,FJo added: "It is so disheartening to
OL,21,Fpeople trying to make this island work.
