OL,6,F"I feel like the States are saying
OL,7,F'yes, maybe, possibly', I feel like
OL,8,Fthey don't care and have left us on
OL,9,Four own."
OL,11,FRepairs to Alderney's airport and
OL,12,Frunway have been ongoing since 1967,
OL,13,Fbut in 2019, the States of Guernsey
OL,14,Fagreed to spend #12.2 million on
OL,15,Fupdating the runway.
OL,17,FThe budget was doubled in 2022 with
OL,18,Fplans to build a new terminal building
OL,19,Fand runway extension.
