OL,3,CAlderney islanders fear they will be
OL,4,Cstranded as airport repairs delayed
OL,6,FDeputy Alex Snowden, States of
OL,7,FAlderney said: "I think there are lots
OL,8,Fof problems with the whole of the
OL,9,FStates of Guernsey and funding capital
OL,10,Fprojects that don't seem to be quite
OL,11,Fmaterialising as the public would
OL,12,Flike. And particularly with the
OL,13,FAlderney runway, safety comes into it.
OL,15,F"If something does happen and if the
OL,16,Frunway was closed for a short or major
OL,17,Famount of time, how is the island
OL,18,Fgoing to be served?"
