OL,6,FDeputy Peter Roffey, States Trading
OL,7,FSupervisory Board added: "The
OL,8,Ftendering process has finished, we
OL,9,Fhave selected a preferred contractor
OL,10,Fto do the work.
OL,12,F"We're now trying to negotiate the
OL,13,Ffinal figure because the tender
OL,14,Fprocess is always the starting point
OL,15,Fand you have post-tender negotiations.
OL,17,F"When that is complete we will be able
OL,18,Fto let people know what is happening
OL,19,Fnext, but it does have to be done in
OL,20,Fconfidence to secure the best deal
OL,21,Fwith the Bailiwick."
